text.tspan: It all started with a trip to Africa...
Since I could become a lion, I thought:
I could hang out with the other lions and that's
what I did. Sleep all day, chase a few gazelles,
I got shot in the butt with a tranq gun!
Everything went fuzzy and the last thing I remember
was this person walking towards me with a gun.
Opening my eyes and all I can see is this cage and a massive
colourful tent. I've been captured by a circus, and I can't
change back into human. I'm stuck!
